Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:16.50,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fnArial\b1\fs42.5\4a&HFF&\pos(960,605)\bord2.2}Ancien plateau royal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:28.10,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fnArial\b1\fs56.5\4a&HFF&\pos(960,550)\bord2.4}Tontatta Airline  –  Scarabées jaunes
